<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وفي <span class="c2">(ص ٣٠٠)</span>: <span class="c1">"ليس بشيء"</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وفي <span class="c2">(ص ٤٤٣)</span>: <span class="c1">"تالف"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
